{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>做个简单的归纳总结，这样下次面试时就有的说了。</p> ","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:03:29","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","sourceUrl":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>1.减少HTTP请求数</p><p>你可以采取雪碧图的方式，或者base64内联图片等资源的方式来减少请求。</p><p>使用HTTP2也可以增加传输效率，加快速度。</p> ","floor":2,"pid":8606,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:07:34","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>2.合理地使用Preload预加载</p><p>当浏览器从上到下加载脚本或css资源的时候，一般是加载一个再执行一个。使用&lt;link rel=preload&gt;可以让浏览器提前加载资源。这样执行起来时就会更快一些。</p> ","floor":3,"pid":8607,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:10:08","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>3.懂得使用缓存</p><p>一般的图片、css和js等各类静态资源都可以使用缓存来减少请求和加快速度。</p><p>通过打包工具将各种资源进行压缩和合并，可以大大减小包体积，减少http请求数，也可以更利于缓存。</p> ","floor":4,"pid":8608,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:12:12","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>4.将不重要的脚本放在页面底部</p><p>例如加载一些发帖框等第三方插件所需要的js代码，如果放在前面的话显而易见是会拖慢页面加载速度的。可以选择把它放在底下，当展示性的内容尽快给用户看了之后，再加载那些用户次要关系的功能性部件。</p> ","floor":5,"pid":8609,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:14:18","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>5.使用lazyload</p><p>购物网站等图片非常多的网页，当用户向下滑动时才开始加载视野内的图片，既节省了服务器贷款流量，也能使用户更快地看到他们目前正在关心的内容。</p> ","floor":6,"pid":8610,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:16:10","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>6.慎用JS动画，使用CSS动画以提高性能</p><p>一般的CSS动画都会有GPU加速以提高性能，使用JS动画的话性能就没那么好了。</p> ","floor":7,"pid":8611,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:17:20","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>7.避免在不断触发的事件内执行大量的代码。</p><p>鼠标的移动事件、窗口的改变大小事件都属于会在一些条件内会不断触发的事件。只在这些事件内执行轻量的代码是提高性能的好办法。另外，也可以使用节流阀之类的技术来减少事件的触发频率。</p> ","floor":8,"pid":8612,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:19:54","replyCount":1,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958,"initComments":{"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"也要避免浏览器频繁地做布局计算。 ","createTime":"2019-04-16 12:30:14","id":3041,"replyId":0,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}}],"pageInfo":{"total":1,"pageSize":10,"current":1},"total":1,"totalPages":1}},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>8.图片一定要压缩之后再放到网站上。</p><p>将图片裁剪成合适的尺寸，压缩至合适的大小，既节省空间和带宽流量，也加速访问速度。</p><p>可以使用CDN来就近分发静态资源。</p> ","floor":9,"pid":8613,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:23:02","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>9.记得配置Gzip压缩</p><p>Gzip压缩在压缩脚本等资源包的时候，可以节省大多数体积。浏览器解压缩的速度也远比传输原始数据来得快。</p> ","floor":10,"pid":8614,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:24:22","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>10.养成良好的JS编写习惯。</p><p>如：避免无用的循环、避免过量的作用域链查找，减少对象和数组的属性操作。</p> ","floor":11,"pid":8615,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:27:15","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"59.56.40.*","authorCode":"","content":"<p>受教了！谢谢分享</p> ","floor":12,"pid":8616,"postTime":"2019-04-23 16:38:15","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958},{"author":"59.64.129.*","authorCode":"","content":"<p>很好</p> ","floor":13,"pid":8825,"postTime":"2020-09-30 21:12:37","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2958}],"pageInfo":{"total":13,"pageSize":30,"current":1},"threadInfo":{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","classifyName":"技术","goodClassifyName":"","id":2958,"isGood":true,"isPicture":false,"isRepost":false,"postTime":"2019-04-16 12:03:29","replyCount":13,"title":"前端性能优化方法总结","topState":0},"tid":2958,"total":13,"totalPages":1,"viewHost":false,"users":{"admin":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}},"needVerify":true}}